JOIN AS AN AGENT Open Menu Close Menu About Us Services Pricing Store Help Contact JOIN AS AN AGENT Frequently Asked Questions What is Cheetah? Cheetah is a modern and innovative online real estate company that offers a model for Our model eliminates transaction fees and provides all services online, allowing agents to increase their income and customize their business as per their preferences worrying about hidden fees or administrative How much does it cost to join Cheetah? Cheetah has three plans for agents: Cheetah Pro at $149 month, Cheetah Pro + at $1499 year. Both plans let agents keep full commission and offer access to tools, resources, support, and Cheetah X is a free plan with % commission for agents and % to Cheetah upon transaction close, perfect for new agents looking for flexibility in real Are there any additional fees other than the subscription? No, there are no additional fees associated with using Cheetah s services other than the subscription What transaction management tools does Cheetah offer? Cheetah provides access to SkySlope, a transaction management software that streamlines the transaction process for What kind of support and training does Cheetah offer? Cheetah offers ongoing support and training to its agents, including webinars, video tutorials, and live chat Does Cheetah provide E&O insurance for agents? Cheetah does not provide individual E&O insurance per agent, however, the company does have its own umbrella insurance It is important to note that agents are required to obtain their own E&O insurance within a reasonable timeframe after E&O insurance provides coverage for potential errors and omissions in real estate transactions and is a standard requirement in the Cheetah can provide guidance and resources to help agents obtain E&O insurance if Does C
